Sentencas: As a mixed ion electronic conducting oxide, PrBaCo2O5+delta is regarded as a promising solid oxide fuel cell cathode.
Titulo: Novel gradient porous cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: To further improve PrBaCo2O5+delta cathode's oxygen reduction reaction activity, porosity graded PrBaCo2O5+delta-based cathode is prepared by screen printing technology.
Titulo: Novel gradient porous cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: With a porous top and a comparative denser base, oxygen ions concentration and oxygen gas concentration in the cathode can be graded distributed.
Titulo: Novel gradient porous cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: This concentration gradient works as driven force which can enhance the cathode catalytic activity.
Titulo: Novel gradient porous cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: And distribution of relaxation time analysis is carried out to investigate cathodes performance optimization mechanism, the result shows that gradient porous PrBaCo2O5+delta cathode's area specific resistance value is much lower than the traditional homogeneous porosity PrBaCo2O5+delta cathode.
Titulo: Novel gradient porous cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The scaffold porosity modification promotes the cathode oxygen ions transfer processes without obvious impact on the cathode oxygen surface processes.
Titulo: Novel gradient porous cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell
